Prepared for trial testimony. Clarified the following: 
• Although . cannot recall every piece of evidence he seized, he specifically recalls 
seizing message pads and twin torpedoes sex toy from 358 El Brillo Way on October 20, 
2005. 
• Photographs of message pads and twin torpedoes from the scene are fair and accurate 
depictions of portions of 358 El Brillo Way as they appeared on October 20, 2005. 
• All evidence, including message pads and twin torpedoes, was turned over to the 
evidence collection team, which was supervised by Crime Scene Manager 
Crime scene team then transported all evidence to PBPD.
